        <p>Track your home’s power usage and optimize energy consumption with real-time insights.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_HOME_DEPOT_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">View on Home Depot</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card US">
        <span class="tag">USA · TOOLS</span>
        <h3>Pro-Grade Tool Set</h3>
        <p>Essential toolkit for home repair, renovation, and infrastructure projects.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_LOWES_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">View on Lowe’s</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card US">
        <span class="tag">USA · TINY AI</span>
        <h3>Tiny AI Sensor Kit</h3>
        <p>Starter kit for experimenting with edge sensors and micro‑controllers.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_AMAZON_US_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">View on Amazon US</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Canada -->
      <div class="card CA">
        <span class="tag">CANADA · HOME ENERGY</span>
        <h3>Smart Thermostat</h3>
        <p>Improve comfort and reduce energy usage with intelligent temperature control.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_CANADA_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">View Canadian Offer</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card CA">
        <span class="tag">CANADA · TOOLS</span>
        <h3>Contractor-Grade Drill Kit</h3>
        <p>Reliable power tool set for home and professional projects.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_LOWES_CANADA_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">View on Lowe’s Canada</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Europe -->
      <div class="card EU">
        <span class="tag">EUROPE · FASHION</span>
        <h3>AI-Ready Streetwear Pack</h3>
        <p>Curated fashion pieces ideal for AI fashion content and digital styling.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_SHEIN_EU_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">Shop SHEIN Europe</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card EU">
        <span class="tag">EUROPE · TECH</span>
        <h3>Compact Solar Power Bank</h3>
        <p>Portable solar charger for travel, remote work, and emergency kits.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_AWIN_EU_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">View European Offer</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Global -->
      <div class="card Global">
        <span class="tag">GLOBAL · TINY AI</span>
        <h3>Nova Sensor Kit</h3>
        <p>Build your own Tiny AI node for experimental energy and data projects.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_ALIEXPRESS_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">Shop AliExpress</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card Global">
        <span class="tag">GLOBAL · FASHION</span>
        <h3>AI Fashion Show Bundle</h3>
        <p>Outfit set curated for AI runway videos and avatar styling.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_SHEIN_GLOBAL_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">Shop Global Fashion</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card Global">
        <span class="tag">GLOBAL · ACCESSORIES</span>
        <h3>Cyber Aesthetic LED Kit</h3>
        <p>Lighting kit for creating futuristic AI studio and runway scenes.</p>
        <a href="YOUR_GLOBAL_AFFILIATE_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn-external">View Global Offer</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="partner-box">
      <strong>BECOME A PARTNER · SSGPT6 AFFILIATE NETWORK</strong>
      <p style="margin:8px 0 4px;">
        Join the SSGPT6 Affiliate & Liaison Network to earn commissions by sharing curated deals and AI-powered tools.
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0;">
        Visit the recruitment portal:
        <a href="affiliate-portal.html">affiliate-portal.html</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal">
      <p>
        SSGPT6 and GNAIAAAC LLC operate as a digital information, media, and affiliate referral platform.
        We do not sell products or process payments. All purchases are completed on third‑party partner
        websites such as retailers, marketplaces, or service providers.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top:6px;">
        Some links on this page may be affiliate links. This means GNAIAAAC LLC may earn a commission if a user
        completes a qualifying purchase through a partner link, at no additional cost to the user.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function filterStore(region){
      const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.geo-selector button');
      buttons.forEach(btn => {
        btn.classList.toggle('active', btn.textContent.includes(region === 'US' ? 'USA' : region));
      });

      const cards = document.querySelectorAll('#product-grid .card');
      cards.forEach(card => {
        if(card.classList.contains(region)){
          card.style.display = 'flex';
        } else {
          card.style.display = 'none';
        }
      });
    }

    // default view
    filterStore('US');
  </script>
</body>
</html>
